_pdbx_database_remark.text   
;SEQUENCE 
Residues 171-182 correspond to residues 1-12 in 
the wild-type structure. The initial 12 residues 
have been moved to the C-terminus, with a 6-residue 
linker (SGGGGA) in between. 
